{
  "stem": "56.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think I brought you up till 1943. 1944 was also very uneventful, except we got used to these selections.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Once you get used to it, it-- it just-- time just goes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You hide.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You-- you try to do your best.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was till 1944. 1944, we-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were evacuated.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They came, again, to the house, and they took everybody out, and they put us on trucks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My brother was not home at the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think he was still working.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Or-- or-- no, he could've been working.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He must have been down the street somewhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they put us on the trucks, and they told us this is-- they told us to take whatever before they put us on the trucks, whatever we want to take with us, whatever.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That we gonna be moved to another camp-- working camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they took us to the station-- to the other side of the ghetto where the station was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, while they had us on the trucks, we heard the Germans yell, stop, stop, stop!",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And all the trucks stopped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And here was a German running with my brother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Even to the last minute, they were such liars.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They just didn't want us to know what's gonna happen, so they said, oh, this young man got separated from his family.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So they were going from truck to truck looking for my brother's family, till they found us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So they-- they just-- it was like a-- a show for the people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They never told the truth.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They never wanted us to know the truth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And from there, they put us on-- into cattle trains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we started our journey-- to where, we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
